Hi Dan,

I just want to say that I hope you’re happy and healthy and that you find whatever it is you need from your hiatus. I miss you 🖤

Thank you, Dan and Phil, for having made me smile.. Without you two and dnpg I wouldn’t have made it through the last 18 months when my adult life fell apart…

Take care (and also please come back sooner or later?)

I love and appreciate you both so much ☀️

@danielhowell @amazingphil
